room_title: Escape room "Vikings" by Time Travel Escapes in West Palm Beach
room_description: We need a team of warriors to travel back in time to the year 1,000 AD to board a Viking merchant ship. Captain Leif Erikson has fallen very ill and will not be able to sail the ship. You will need to work as a team and use both decks of the ship to complete tasks. You and your crew must find all the clues and figure out how to chart your way back home to save his life.
